cs.CR, cs.SE, cs.PL, cs.SY, cs.AI 

The paper discusses a technique for automatically generating and mutating inputs for unknown chunk-based binary formats, which is a topic related to security (cs.CR) and software engineering (cs.SE). The paper also proposes a technique to identify dependencies between input bytes and comparison instructions, which involves program analysis (cs.PL) and machine learning (cs.AI). Finally, the paper presents a prototype implementation that reveals unknown bugs in widely used programs, which is related to systems and control (cs.SY).
